query:
SELECT hm.id as memberId, hm.memberName, h.id as householdId, h.name as householdName 
FROM household_members hm 
JOIN households h ON hm.householdId = h.id 
WHERE h.name = 'Buchenb端hl' AND hm.memberName = 'Basti';
